9. Scope Boundaries Document 
Included Within Scope:
•	Reporting of cybersecurity incidents by employees
•	Triage, assignment, and tracking of incidents
•	Guided response workflows for common incident types
•	Real-time dashboard for monitoring incident status
•	Notifications and alerts
•	Reporting and analytics for incidents
•	User authentication and role-based access control

Excluded from Scope:
•	Network monitoring and intrusion detection
•	Vulnerability assessment and scanning
•	Automated incident remediation
•	Integration with third-party threat intelligence
•	Mobile application for incident reporting
System Boundaries:
The system is a web-based application focused on the management of cybersecurity incidents from reporting to resolution. It does not include proactive threat detection or automated response actions.
